sentences.english: I teach English Language Skills at Tianjin Teda Maple Leaf International School.
sentences.chinese: 目前在天津泰達楓葉國際學校教授英文。

sentences.english: The TEDA International Hospital will be a modern hospital specializing cardiovascular diseases.
sentences.chinese: 泰達國際醫院將成爲現代化的心血管專科醫院。

sentences.english: TEDA Watson Bio-tech Park is a specialized incubator established by overseas scholars.
sentences.chinese: 泰達華生生物園是由歸國留學生創建的專業孵化器。

sentences.english: Highlights of the opening round included home wins for Hangzhou Lucheng and Tianjin Teda.
sentences.chinese: 首輪比賽精選包括杭州綠城和天津泰達主場獲勝。

sentences.english: There will be a CFA Cup semi-final in Tianjin between TEDA and Shanghai tonight.
sentences.chinese: 今晚足協盃半決賽天津泰達將主場對陣上海申花。

sentences.english: Thank you for visiting Tianjin (TEDA) Maple Leaf International School on-line.
sentences.chinese: 歡迎您在線訪問天津泰達楓葉國際學校。

sentences.english: After the last outage, the TEDA Railway Station has been turned off.
sentences.chinese: 自去年停運之後，泰達火車站一直處於關閉狀態。
